<br>
Here's a very samuraiesque style that appeals to me/<br>
<br>
Deathblow<br>
<br>
Preq: Weapons must be sheathed.<br>
Timer: 5min<br>
Effect: When you hit this your weapons draw and you hit with an instant swipe that does about 4 or 5times normal damage as a regular blow maybe more.<br>
<br>
To me this would be very useful in those first few painful seconds of caster and healer killing and will deal with that enchater pbaoe;ing you in a hurry.<br>
<br>
Rock Throw<br>
<br>
Preq: weapons must be sheathed(cant throw rocks with hands occupied)<br>
Timer: 3min<br>
Effect low damage insta that works at about half a bolts range that stops castin for ten seconds.<br>
<br>
Now this is rogueish. We can throw mud why not rocks? This helps the hardest part of being an offensive tank, getting to the caster or mezzer to even do soemthing about him/her.<br>
<br>
Kick Off<br>
<br>
Timer 5min<br>
<br>
Effect: low damage and pushes target back 5-10 paces stuns for four.<br>
<br>
Another rogueish kind of ability.  Big warrior givin ya problems as you beat down the skald? kick him away.  Though i think resists can be put into affect for guys who carry a shield or have a much higher strength. i.e.: Kicking the troll with a saracean was a bad idea.<br>
<br>
ill come up with more later as i think about em. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showMessageRange?topicID=268.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showMessageRange?topicID=268.topic&start=41&stop=58>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=268.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=268.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=268.topic&index=35><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=268.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.threadControl?topicID=268.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=268.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=268.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email noti